Extension: Extension : Item Settings

Official URL: https://science37.github.io/FHIR-FSH-Implementation-Guide/StructureDefinition/item-settings Version: 1.0.0-S37
Active as of 2022-04-22 Computable Name: ItemSettings

Extension : Questionnaire.item.settings

Context of Use

This extension may be used on the following element(s):

  • Questionnaire.item

Usage info

Usage:

  • Derived from this Extension: Extension : DateTimeItem Settings , Extension : DerivedItem Settings , Extension : VASScaleItem Settings
  • Use this Extension: Profile : Questionnaire.item extensions
  • Examples for this Extension: Example : Questionnaire.Item, Example : Questionnaire.Item FileUpload, Example : Questionnaire.Item Footer, Example : Questionnaire.Item Header, Example : Questionnaire.Item Image, Example : Questionnaire.Item MultiSelect, Example : Questionnaire.Item Number-Decimal, Example : Questionnaire.Item Number-Integer, Example : Questionnaire.Item RatingScale, Example : Questionnaire.Item RichText, Example : Questionnaire.Item Select, Example : Questionnaire.Item Text, Example : Questionnaire.Item TextArea, Example : Questionnaire.Item derived, Example : Questionnaire.Item page-break
